                            <div class="thumbnail">
                                <img src="img/awards/miup2012_thumb.jpg"
                                    alt="From left to right, Diogo Sousa, David Serrano, Daniel Parreira and Margarida Mamede, being the MIUP&apos;12 bronze medalists">
                            </div>
                        </li>
                    </ul>
                    <h4>Bronze Medal (fifth place), on the team
